title: "Knowledge Persistence Architectures for AI-Based Coding Agents: Replication Package"
abstract: "Replication package for a systematic literature review (PRISMA 2020) on knowledge persistence architectures for AI-based coding agents. Contains the final search strategy, saved database exports, citation-chasing records, deduplication ledger, screening decisions, structured extraction data for 95 included records, synthesis tables, and PRISMA flow source."
